    narr:childCount "122"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "11698bdcc99e773321dbed09556ee1e1736a3866" ;
    narr:narration """The positioning of aswritten has shifted from a capability-led enterprise tool to a [CEO context-server reframe](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CEOContextServerReframe) that eliminates the invisible tax on leadership. The foundational category remains [expertise installation](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CategoryCuratedExpertiseInstallation), now framed as the [third era of knowledge distribution](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TrustedInformationEra). The product is defined as the [memory substrate](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AswrittenIsMemorySubstrate) for [steering decision processes](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SteeringDecisionProcess), explicitly rejecting governance as a category. Market focus has evolved from enterprise to a [B2C primary](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_B2CPivot) model, reconciled by the [tier-continuum resolution](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TierContinuumNotDistinctMarkets) where expert, team, and org are a single use case. Recent work emphasizes [individually owned AGI](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_IndividuallyOwnedAGIReclaim) and the [anti-monoculture amplifier](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AntiMonocultureAmplifier) thesis. The go-to-market now favors [consulting-as-infrastructure](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConsultingIsMeUsingProduct), where the client never touches the tool. While [transcript bootstrapping](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TranscriptBootstrappingUnderplayed) remains a vital onramp, it has been [qualified by three demotions](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TranscriptDemotionFrictionNotValue): transcripts are friction, not value; pain leads the story.""" ;
